Subject: [PATCH 40/56] LF-15823: arm64: dts: imx95-15x15-frdm: Enable BOE WXGA
 LVDS panel

Enable BOE WXGA LVDS panel for FRDM-IMX95 board.

Signed-off-by: Lei Xu <lei.xu@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Joseph Guo <qijian.guo@nxp.com>
Acked-by: Liu Ying <victor.liu@nxp.com>
Reviewed-by: Bough Chen <haibo.chen@nxp.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile        |  2 +-
 .../imx95-15x15-frdm-boe-wxga-lvds-panel.dts  | 99 +++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 100 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
 create mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/imx95-15x15-frdm-boe-wxga-lvds-panel.dts

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
index 05885b69a44f..123c1640fcf1 100644
